{"tid":1874789,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支那禁稱「武漢肺炎」惹議　維基百科出現「新冠市」反制","createTime":"2020-02-11T11:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T14:30:44.000Z","uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"409e6542922530d90f33d2865acacf3b1b2bfe63","tid":1874789,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"大陸日前以防止污名化為由，禁止稱呼「武漢肺炎」，一律改稱「新冠肺炎」；有網友不滿此一決定，便把維基百科中武漢市條目改成「新冠市」，以示抗議。<br />\n <br />\n儘管武漢肺炎的疫情已經相當嚴重，但大陸仍非常重視門面，其國務院8日以防止污名化為由，召開記者會宣布禁止稱呼「武漢肺炎」，一聲令下，大陸中央宣傳部、國務院台灣辦公室、港澳事務辦公室等單位隨即通令業管宣傳單位即日起更改「武漢肺炎」為「新冠肺炎」。<br />\n <br />\n不過，大陸官方越是在意這些表面問題，反而越讓外界關注。不僅丹麥漫畫把五星旗改成「五毒旗」，時代雜誌封面把習近平戴上大口罩，華盛頓郵報甚至譏諷大陸是「亞洲病夫」。<br />\n <br />\n除了上述各種嘲諷外，也有人發現，維基百科上武漢市條目竟然被改成「新冠市」，而且在條目的內容之中，文字說明也被改成：「新冠市，舊稱武漢，簡稱漢，別稱江漢&hellip;」。<br />\n <br />\n本刊獨家找到進行修改動作的網友Andy，詢問其背後動機，他解釋：「覺得中國硬要別人叫新冠病毒，以求跟中國脫鉤，很蠢而已。」<br />\n <br />\n此外，也有網友表示，香港腳、德國麻疹、日本腦炎、蒙古症也都有地名、國名，大陸怎麼不一起改一改？更有網友說，日本北海道有新冠郡、新冠町，大陸取名「新冠肺炎」害他們躺著也中槍。<br />\n <br />\n截稿時，維基百科已更正相關條目。"},{"pid":"16a5f79ff7707e02194d43a0001d25347df46e65","tid":1874789,"uid":254183,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/if6Ognr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fif6Ognr.jpg&h=2e686c2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"825b5e7bde54dc311a27c1f67b10c37246d1e933","tid":1874789,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587509d0589e1a8d0fb73055c42a769509059b06","tid":1874789,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />home of umbrella cooroperation<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58457bc5b97bcd3b06d4a2d3ae78da844fa0eace","tid":1874789,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9YUbXv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9YUbXv.png&h=1d1f8312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本真係有個新冠町<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a91b52f6010cd8efba161516d84acdffea5aa0f","tid":1874789,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"正如將「非禮罪」避禕成「森美罪」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1a1-1024x683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2F1a1-1024x683.jpg&h=69a21ac9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11a21815d0c109d4bb761ede70ce4e0cdd7d0106","tid":1874789,"uid":275161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"啱呀 叫支那肺炎"},{"pid":"31eb0e297d297dfd116fca9b8c107256ddf2b921","tid":1874789,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a21815d0c109d4bb761ede70ce4e0cdd7d0106","tid":1874789,"uid":275161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"啱呀 叫支那肺炎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"個名聽落好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffffe5c3197637775de456d409ee9d856966d68","tid":1874789,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"香港腳呢"},{"pid":"40d33489f19fe2de2a6912b874391bd5619c5087","tid":1874789,"uid":258696,"l